.SH "NAME"
Bio::AlignIO::mega \- Parse and Create MEGA format data files
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 3
\&    use Bio::AlignIO;
\&    my $alignio = Bio::AlignIO\->new(\-format => \*(Aqmega\*(Aq,
\&                                   \-file   => \*(Aqt/data/hemoglobinA.meg\*(Aq);
\&
\&    while( my $aln = $alignio\->next_aln ) {
\&    # process each alignment or convert to another format like NEXUS
\&    }
.Ve
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This object handles reading and writing data streams in the \s-1MEGA\s0
format (Kumar and Nei).
